227
00:13:30.548 --> 00:13:32.688
And when we're conducting the stratified analysis,

228
00:13:33.668 --> 00:13:37.248
we can see that the association between our signature

229
00:13:37.388 --> 00:13:39.048
score and the lung cancer risk

230
00:13:39.908 --> 00:13:43.668
shows the consistent patterns across strata by the site,

231
00:13:44.068 --> 00:13:47.888
