232
00:13:48.008 --> 00:13:48.708
lung cancer.

233
00:13:50.028 --> 00:13:53.688
More importantly, we can see that the association remains

234
00:13:53.708 --> 00:13:57.588
significant among the long-term quitters who quit at least 20 years,

235
00:13:58.228 --> 00:14:01.668
and these participants are not eligible to the lung cancer

236
00:14:01.728 --> 00:14:03.818
