237
00:14:05.888 --> 00:14:09.368
We further evaluate the predictive performance of our

238
00:14:09.388 --> 00:14:10.048
signature.

239
00:14:10.888 --> 00:14:14.778
So as you know, the PLCOM 2012 is a validated

240
00:14:15.108 --> 00:14:18.988
