And the model is mainly based on the self-report information, such

243
00:14:24.968 --> 00:14:28.018
as the demographic, clinical, and detailed smoking history.

244
00:14:29.828 --> 00:14:33.628
And you can see that adding our signature to the PLCOM

245
00:14:33.748 --> 00:14:37.188
2012 models significantly improved the predictive

246
00:14:37.208 --> 00:14:40.888
