248
00:14:44.948 --> 00:14:47.748
50 years or over 20 years since quit smoking.

249
00:14:49.948 --> 00:14:53.928
We further validate our signature

250
00:14:54.048 --> 00:14:57.728
using the 71 case control nested within the

251
00:14:57.788 --> 00:14:59.608
