255
00:15:11.548 --> 00:15:15.528
show the strong association with the increased

256
00:15:15.588 --> 00:15:16.708
risk of lung cancer.

257
00:15:18.228 --> 00:15:21.868
Additionally, when we adjust for the smoking pack year or years since quit

258
00:15:21.968 --> 00:15:25.688
smoking, we still see the significant association.

259
00:15:28.028 --> 00:15:28.468
Excuse me.

