507
00:30:21.122 --> 00:30:25.062
So here on the right, we highlight the 10 pathways

508
00:30:25.402 --> 00:30:28.462
that overlap with either ERG or lethal status.

509
00:30:28.902 --> 00:30:32.234
And this is mostlyMarked

510
00:30:32.294 --> 00:30:35.734
by increased translation or

