Yeah.

610
00:36:16.834 --> 00:36:18.814
I think yeah, it's a great question.

611
00:36:18.934 --> 00:36:19.194
So,

612
00:36:20.274 --> 00:36:21.414
definitely there's,

613
00:36:22.674 --> 00:36:25.694
for example, height PRS showed a great

