00:36:26.634 --> 00:36:30.534
performance, but it still only explain 50% of the heritability.

615
00:36:31.334 --> 00:36:33.686
Um-But I think

616
00:36:35.326 --> 00:36:35.446
the

617
00:36:36.586 --> 00:36:38.226
results that we see here,

618
