810
00:48:25.726 --> 00:48:28.906
Yes. So this was actually using DNA methylation array data.

811
00:48:29.086 --> 00:48:29.096
Okay.

812
00:48:29.096 --> 00:48:32.946
So we were able to assess any copy number alterations based off

813
00:48:33.046 --> 00:48:35.146
