816
00:48:43.186 --> 00:48:47.005
alterations. And then we implemented autocorrection steps as well to

817
00:48:47.046 --> 00:48:51.006
help normalize to the overall baseline to ensure that what we're

818
00:48:51.066 --> 00:48:54.646
actually seeing are copy number alterations, are copy number

819
00:48:54.706 --> 00:48:56.826
alterations, if that answers your question.

820
00:48:56.986 --> 00:48:57.546
Yes. Thank you.

821
00:48:57.726 --> 00:48:58.146
Thank you.

822
00:49:01.498 --> 00:49:02.518
I have a couple questions-

823
00:49:02.538 --> 00:49:02.628
Yes

824
00:49:02.628 --> 00:49:03.198
... if you don't mind.

