00:49:26.578 --> 00:49:30.418
There have been research studies showing that they are very comparable and

834
00:49:30.458 --> 00:49:32.518
highly correlated to SNP genotyping-

835
00:49:33.878 --> 00:49:33.888
Okay

836
00:49:33.888 --> 00:49:35.078
... for copy number calling.

837
00:49:35.878 --> 00:49:39.738
One of the caveats is that from the methylation Epic array, we are

